# Razorpay (for later)
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID="..."
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET="..."
RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET="..."

# App Config
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"
```

**Deliverables**:
- `.env.local` configured
- `.env.example` template created

