## Phase 7: Subscriptions & Monetization

### 7.1 Subscription Tiers

**Tiers**:
| Tier | Price (INR) | Quizzes | Features |
|------|-------------|---------|----------|
| Free | 0 | 1 | MCQs only, teaser quiz |
| Basic | 99 | 3 | MCQs only |
| Pro | 299 | 10 | Full hands-on + AI reports |
| Elite | 499 | 20 | + Mentorship + unlimited retries |

**Implementation**:
1. Pricing page ([app/pricing/page.tsx](file:///d:/Gautam%20Khatri%20-%20DA%20mentorship/QuizPro-Platform/app/pricing/page.tsx))
2. Razorpay integration (`app/api/webhooks/razorpay/route.ts`)
3. Webhook handler to update `subscriptionTier` in Prisma
4. Middleware to check quota before quiz generation

**Deliverables**:
- Pricing page
- Payment integration
- Quota enforcement

